{"tid":2019987,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中銀短訊疑似「呃人」 發言人：不會透過短訊收集個人資料","createTime":"2020-05-16T16:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T08:54:12.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a72cdf508736da43e323bbe8bfd384c7cb62e75","tid":2019987,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"有人在社交媒體群組瘋傳一個疑似偽冒中銀香港（2388）發出的短訊，並附有「小心，唔好亂按，我朋友個太太琴日先中咗招，畀人拎咗Whatsapp賬戶和聯絡人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」提醒字句。中銀香港發言人表示，注意到坊間傳言，強調不會透過短訊收集個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200515/large/1589534414_7d71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200515%2Flarge%2F1589534414_7d71.jpg&h=95da61da&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200515/A64LDGPE2CNGJMQYZL6PUME4BI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200515%2FA64LDGPE2CNGJMQYZL6PUME4BI%2F&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BfE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=fdbc7b1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200515%2FA64LDGPE2CNGJMQYZL6PUME4BI%2F&h=4bf6d7d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200515/A64LDGPE2CNGJMQYZL6PUME4BI/</a>"},{"pid":"416519de77a1370c464ae8213a56cb1b60607ef1","tid":2019987,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:23:05.000Z","msg":"姐係係<br />\n<br />\n用中資抵撚死"},{"pid":"b29cca5118933735a2458e5a963b29a2d93d65e7","tid":2019987,"uid":321854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一早CUT左"},{"pid":"2bafeb1ff783a9be60af344ff6e0a0c9c97ebaed","tid":2019987,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"多名市民近日相繼收到一個聲稱由「中銀香港BOCHK」發出的短訊，內容提醒市民做好準備登記領取政府派發的1萬元，透過電子渠道登記可更快收取款項，並附有一個網址，呼籲大家「立即按此先重啟手機銀行」。<br />\n<br />\n然而，有網民卻截圖在網上指，有友人的妻子「琴日先中左（咗）招」，聲稱按下有關連結後，WhatsApp帳戶及聯絡人資料被盜取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，需要即時更換sim卡，其後更收到大量詐騙電話和信息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，呼籲大家「小心，唔好亂按」；另有網民聲指該短訊並非由中銀發出，在網上呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n    「請勿打開上面網址！！它會偷取你的電話簿內所有資料，再覆製轉發」<br />\n<br />\n中銀發言人回覆《晴報》則確認曾發出相關短訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但強調不會透過短訊收集個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"d01211ef5c7afabca586edfee56848f6a7480a76","tid":2019987,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:26:17.000Z","msg":"有撚關係咩<br />\n8個number 得幾千萬個組合<br />\n啲廣告電話逐個打一定中你架啦"},{"pid":"3ed725b6e59f419bbef58792677b8943a03b503b","tid":2019987,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"[黃色經濟圈] 點睇淘寶&yen;9.9嘅款要賣成$248？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2019896\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2019896</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7c2a3796fbf192367fbf36fda7ef05ef0917895","tid":2019987,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:32:25.000Z","msg":"一定好多人中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d848b4f87778368ce0b66726810e49faf18cab54","tid":2019987,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"個sms 係真<br />\n不過太輕挑, 唔似銀行d formal <br />\n用中銀抵撚死, 無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee